room_title: Escape room "House Of Voodoo" by Nightmare at 3008 in Birmingham
room_description: Come see the House of Voodoo! Laissez les bons temps rouler! (Let the good times roll!) You are about to experience the good and the bad of the bayou. Be careful and DO NOT look into the eyes of the lost, you may get caught up and your soul will become ours!
